videos.description: Eric Dungey's is picked off by Hurricane's DL Demetrius Jackson who is immediately stripped by Dungey.

videos.description: Eric Dungey's pass is intercepted by Michael Jackson and he and his teammates celebrate with the turnover chain on the sidelines.

videos.description: Malik Rosier completes to Christopher Herndon IV for a 10-yard touchdown to extend the Hurricanes' lead.
videos.headline: Rosier finds Johnson in the end zone

videos.description: Jaquan Johnson picks off Eric Dungey on the Miami 38-yard line and the Hurricanes celebrate again with the turnover chain.
videos.headline: Miami wears the turnover chain again after Dungey throws his 3rd pick

videos.headline: Babers: 'Excited about what we can do in the second half'

videos.headline: Neal responds with an Orange TD
